    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Members of a family containing about 40 species of oceanic fish found worldwide in warm waters and noted for their ability to fly or glide by using winglike, rigid fins and an unevenly forked tail.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
